content.rendered:
Directed By Amrit Raj Chadha. Santosh Subhash Thite

Written By Surinder Angural. Rupinder Inderjit

Stars Neeru Bajwa (Billo). Rubina Bajwa (Sonika). Roshan Prince (Navi). Rup Khatkar (Sonam). Honey Mattu. Rupinder Rupi. Sukhwinder Chahal. Jatinder Kaur. Baninder Bunny (Baji Rao Barmingham). Raghveer Boli (Shinda).

Language Punjabi

Producer Sukhjeet Jaito. Zeerak Seharai

Production Neeru Bajwa Entertainment. Omjee Star Studios. Sarin Productions
